12:["$","$L13",null,{"slug":"analytics","locale":"es","content":{"metaTitle":"Marketing Analytics Pricing | Transparent Plans | KINEXIS Digital","metaDescription":"Transparent marketing analytics pricing with clear tiers and deliverables. No hidden fees. No vague retainers.","hero":{"label":"Marketing Analytics Pricing","line1":"Marketing Analytics Pricing","line2":"without the guesswork.","subtitle":"Fixed scope at each tier. You see what is included before you sign anything."},"answerBlock":"Most marketing teams are flying blind. They have data on page views, session counts, and ad impressions, but they can't answer the questions that actually matter: which channel booked the last 20 customers, what the cost per qualified lead is by source, or which content is driving pipeline vs. just traffic. Setup projects are billed separately from ongoing reporting retainers.","tiers":[{"name":"Starter","range":"$$2,000","description":"GA4 + GTM setup, 3 conversion goals, and a single Looker Studio dashboard. One-time project.","bestFor":"GA4 + GTM setup, 3 conversion goals, and a single Looker Studio dashboard. One-time project."},{"name":"Growth","range":"$$4,000/mo","description":"Full tracking stack, multi-channel attribution, CRM integration, and monthly reporting.","bestFor":"Full tracking stack, multi-channel attribution, CRM integration, and monthly reporting."},{"name":"Scale","range":"$$6,500+/mo","description":"Enterprise analytics with custom attribution models, data warehouse, and exec reporting suite.","bestFor":"Enterprise analytics with custom attribution models, data warehouse, and exec reporting suite."}],"tiersSection":{"title":"Investment guidance","subtitle":"Pricing based on stack complexity and reporting needs.","note":"Setup projects are billed separately from ongoing reporting retainers."},"included":["Analytics Audit","GA4 Configuration","GTM Implementation","Conversion Tracking","Dashboard Build","Monthly Reporting"],"includedSection":{"title":"What's included","subtitle":"Full analytics setup from tracking infrastructure through dashboards and attribution.","items":[{"title":"Analytics Audit","description":"Full review of current GA4, GTM, and ad platform tracking for gaps, errors, and data quality issues."},{"title":"GA4 Configuration","description":"Clean GA4 setup with proper event taxonomy, conversion goals, and enhanced measurement."},{"title":"GTM Implementation","description":"Tag management setup with organized triggers, variables, and tags for every tracking requirement."},{"title":"Conversion Tracking","description":"Form submissions, phone calls, purchases, and offline conversions tracked across all channels."},{"title":"Dashboard Build","description":"Looker Studio or native dashboards showing leads, CPL, ROAS, and channel attribution in one view."},{"title":"Monthly Reporting","description":"Regular performance analysis with actionable recommendations, not just data exports."}]},"comparison":{"title":"Investment guidance","subtitle":"Pricing based on stack complexity and reporting needs.","layout":"progression","columns":[{"header":"Starter","highlight":false},{"header":"Growth","highlight":true},{"header":"Scale","highlight":false}],"rows":[{"label":"Analytics Audit","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"GA4 Configuration","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"GTM Implementation","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Conversion Tracking","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Best for","values":["GA4 + GTM setup, 3 conversion goals, and a single Looker Studio dashboard. One-time project.","Full tracking stack, multi-channel attribution, CRM integration, and monthly reporting.","Enterprise analytics with custom attribution models, data warehouse, and exec reporting suite."]},{"label":"Starting investment","values":["$$2,000","$$4,000/mo","$$6,500+/mo"]}]},"faqs":[{"question":"Is there a setup fee?","answer":"Most engagements include onboarding and strategy in month one. We quote it upfront. No surprise charges on the first invoice."},{"question":"Do you require a long-term contract?","answer":"No. Month to month. Results should earn your business, not a contract clause."},{"question":"What affects my price?","answer":"Setup projects are billed separately from ongoing reporting retainers."},{"question":"Can I start with a smaller plan and upgrade?","answer":"Yes. Many clients start on Starter and move up once momentum builds. We plan the upgrade path so you are not rebuilding from scratch."},{"question":"¿Con qué herramientas analíticas trabajan?","answer":"GA4, Google Tag Manager, Looker Studio, HubSpot, Salesforce y analítica nativa de plataformas de anuncios. Construimos dashboards en la herramienta que tu equipo ya usa o recomendamos la mejor opción."},{"question":"¿Cuánto cuesta la gestión de analítica de marketing?","answer":"Retainers van de $1,500 a $3,500 al mes según cantidad de canales, integraciones y complejidad de reportes. Proyectos únicos de setup GA4 y dashboards parten en $3,000."},{"question":"¿Pueden corregir nuestro setup GA4 existente?","answer":"Sí. La mayoría de cuentas que auditamos tienen eventos faltantes, conversiones duplicadas o conexiones CRM rotas. Normalmente resolvemos problemas core de tracking en 2 a 3 semanas."},{"question":"¿Reportan ROI y ROAS?","answer":"Sí, cuando la integración CRM está en su lugar. Reportamos costo por lead, costo por adquisición, ROAS por canal y valor de pipeline atribuido a campañas de marketing."}],"ctaHeadline":"Want a quote for marketing analytics?","ctaSubtitle":"Tell us your goals, market, and scope.|We will recommend the right tier and show you what the first 90 days look like.","ctaLabel":"Get Marketing Analytics Pricing"},"serviceHref":"/services/analytics","serviceLabel":"Marketing Analytics Services","breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Home","url":"/"},{"name":"Services","url":"/services"},{"name":"Marketing Analytics Services","url":"/services/analytics"},{"name":"Marketing Analytics Pricing"}]}]
